com.inrix.sdk.utils

Class TimeVariant

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.utils.TimeVariant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITimeVariant

    public class TimeVariant
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITimeVariant
    Wrapper class for a system date / time. Mostly to encapsulate the existing system APIs for obtaining current time and date (as it's not easy to mock them). http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Delegation_pattern
